        &lt;h2&gt;Purpose&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;purpose&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#purpose&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;word4c is a 4c client program that interfaces with Microsoft Word&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Usage&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;usage&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
